====== H6629: צֹאן ======

===== Source =====

or   ; (Psalm 144:13), from an unused root meaning to  ;

===== Meaning =====

migrate a collective name for a  flock  (of sheep or goats); also figuratively (of men)

===== Definitions =====

  - migrate
  - flock

===== Usage =====

(small) cattle, flock (  -s), lamb (  -s), sheep(-cote, -fold, -shearer, -herds).
